msg: Checked in LdapUserDatabase, and refactorings to other LDAP classes. The LdapUserDatabase is read-only. ProfileTab will respect this will print, rather than allow edits to, user profile information as a result. Any UserDatabase can now be flagged as "read-only" (via jspwiki.properties) to achieve the same effect.
